name: Where’d you go?…
description:
Where’d you go? I was just beside you. We held our breath with our eyes closed, suffocating in an overwhelming state of bliss.  And in turning blue, only the heart was left to remain.

Now I’m here, counting the days.  Stranded. Waiting. Waiting for you to come back, as winds blow and waves lap…
